---
title: Roast Chicken in Red Wine Mushroom Sauce with garlic mash and carrots
description: Succulent chicken breast is roasted to perfection and served alongside tender carrots and garlicky mashed potato, all topped off in a rich and delicious red wine mushroom sauce in this impressive weeknight meal.
